thread.title: Malena McDaniel
thread.title_full: The Logo Boutique reviewed by Malena McDaniel

author: Malena McDaniel
title: Malena McDaniel
text:
Communications were often and the deliverables on time. Always professional and great at incorporating my comments.
I have the perfect logo for my business now. The 3 concepts were beautiful and great, they quickly responded with revisions and I was always pleased.
They took my description of the business, and what my ideas were, and made it an image.
I recommend 100%.
